[{"Id": 1016654, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "The meaning of allegiance between two parties is the commitment of the one who pledges allegiance, and his firm vow and strong covenant that he will support the person with whom he has pledged allegiance through his life and wealth, and does not commit any mistake in what he performs for him, and assist him to whatever extent he can, and sacrifice his life and wealth for safeguarding him. And the allegiance of this meaning has been mentioned in the supplication of Ahad which should be recited daily, and in the supplication of Ahad which should be recited continuously for 40 days. And the Holy Prophet (s) had invited all the people, irrespective of those who were present or not, during his sermon of Ghadeer towards such allegiance with the Holy Infallibles (a). Doubtlessly, such an allegiance is one of the conditions and signs of faith, or rather, without it faith cannot be accomplished. The person who pledges allegiance (the seller) is a believer, and the purchaser is the Almighty Allah. Therefore, He said in the Holy Qur’an (9:111) that…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ahad o Paiymaan aur Baiyat ka maani (matlab) o mafhoom yaani pa-band hona dar haqeeqat baiyat karne waala is baat ka mustahkam ahed karta hai keh jiski us ne baiyat ki hai uski raah mein jaan-maal sabhi kuchh qurbaan karega, bal-keh us se jis tarah bhi mumkin hoga unki nusrat mein kotaahi na karega. Har roz padhi jaane waali Dua-e-Ahad mein jo baiyat hai uska aur dusri dua-e-ahad jisko 40 subh padhne ke liya kaha gaya hai us mein jo baiyat hai dono ka maani ek hai. Rasool-e-Khuda (s) ne poori ummat ko hukm diya hai ke tamaam Aimma (a) ke saath aisi hi baiyat kare aur kitaab Ehtejaaj ki riwaayat mein Khutba-e-Ghadeer ke andar ummat ke haazreen aur ghaaebeen ko aisi hi baiyat ka hukm diya gaya hai, bila-shuba aisi baiyat imaan ka laazma aur uski nishaani hai bal-keh dar-haqeeqat aisi baiyat ke bagair imaan paiyda nahi ho sakta. Haa’n, is jagah baiyat karne waala bandah momeen hai aur kharidaar Khuda hai is liye Khudawand-e-Aalam Quran-e-Majeed (9:111) mein farmata hai…", "UrduDescription": "بیعت کا معنی اور مفہوم اپنے آپ کو پابند کرنا ہے واقعے میں عھد موکّد اور بیعت کرنے والا محکم عہد کرے اس پر کہ جس کی بیعت کرتاہے اس کی جان اور مال کے ساتھ اسکی مدد کرے اس راستے میں جو کچھ اس کے ہاتھ آٹاہے اس میں کوتاہی نہ کرے اپنیجان اور مال کو اس شخص کی حفاظت میں قربان کرے اور وہ بیعت کہ جو دعائئے عھد میں ہر روزپڑھی جاتی ہے اور دوسری دعائے عہد کے ۴۰ دن کے وقت پڑھی جاتی ہے اس بیعت کا یہی معنی ہے پیغمبر خدا نے تمام امت کو حکم دیا ہے کہا س قسم کی بیعت تمام اماموں کے ساتھ انجام دیں وہاں خطبہ غدیر میں کہ جو کتاب الاحتجاج میں روایت ہوئی ہے کہ حاضرین اور غائبین کو اپنی بیعت پر مامور فرمایا ہے اس میں کوئی شک نہیں ہے کہ ایسی بیعت ایمان کے لوازم اور ایمان کی علامتوں میں سے ہے بلکہ واقعیت میں ایمان اس بیعت کے بغیر ثابت نہیں ہوتاہے۔ کیوں نہیں۔ یہاں بیچنے والا مومن اور خریدنے والا اللہ تعالیٰ ہے اس لئے خدا نے قرآن میں فرمایا ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016655, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Surely Allah has bought of the believers their persons and their property for this, that they shall have the garden…", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Be-shak Allah ne sahebaan'e imaan se unke jaan o maal ko Jannat ke ewaz (badle) kharid liya hai…", "Urdu": "بےشک اللہ نے صاحبان ایمان سے ان کے جان و مال کو جنت کے بدلے خرید لیا ہے۔۔۔", "RArabic": "INNAL LAA-HASH TARAA MINAL MOMENEENA AN-FOSA-HUM WA AMWAA LA-HUM BE-ANNA LAHO-MUL JANNATA…", "ArabicText1": "اِنَّ اللهَ اشْتَرٰى مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ اَنْفُسَهُمْ وَاَمْوَالَهُمْ بِاَنَّ لَهُمُ الْجَنَّةَ۔۔۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016656, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Allah (swt) has sent down the Prophets and Messengers for the purpose of renewing this allegiance, and to lay emphasis on it. Therefore, whoever pledges allegiance to them, has pledged allegiance to Allah. And whoever turns away from them, has turned himself away from Allah. Hence, Allah said in the Holy Qur’an (48:10)…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Dar-Haqeeqat Parwardigaar-e-Aalam ne apne Ambiya (a) aur Rasool (a) ko is baiyat ki tajdeed (yaad-dahaani) aur uski taakeed ki hai aur jo un se rukh modey us ne dar-haqeeqat Khuda se rukh moda hai is liye Parwardigaar-e-Aalam Quran-e-Majeed (48:10) mein farmata hai…", "UrduDescription": "خدا نے مومنین کی جان اور مال کو بہشت کے مقابلہ میں خریدا ہے سچ مچ خداوند متعال نے پیغمبروں اور رسولوں کو تجدید عہد اور بیعت کے لئے بھیجا ہے پس جو بھی ائمہ معصومین کی بیعت کرے واقع میں اس نے خدا کی بیعت کی ہے اور جو ان سے روگردانی کرے تو حقیقت میں خدا سے روگردانی کی ہے اس لئے خدا قرآن مجید میں فرماتاہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016657, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Surely those who swear allegiance to you do but swear allegiance to Allah; the hand of Allah is above their hands. Therefore whoever breaks (his faith), he breaks it only to the injury of his own soul, and whoever fulfills what he has covenanted with Allah, He will grant him a mighty reward.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Be-shak jo log aap ki baiy’at (aap se waada) karte hai woh dar-haqeeqat Allah ki baiy’at karte hai aur unke haatho’n ke upar Allah hi ka haath hai ab uske baad jo baiy’at ko tod deta hai woh apne hi khilaaf iqdaam karta hai aur jo ahed'e ilaahi ko pura karta hai Khuda an-qareeb usi ko ajr'e azeem ataa karega.", "Urdu": " اے رسول جو بھی تیری بیعت کرتے ہیں واقع میں خدا کی بیعت کرتے ہیں خدا کا ہاتھ تمام ہاتھوں کے اوپر ہے جو بھی اس پیمان اور عہد کو توڑدے واقع میں اپنے خلاف عہد کو توڑا ہے اور جو بھی اس عہد اور پیمان پر خدا کے ساتھ باندھہے اور وہ وفادار ہیں عنقریب اس کو بہت بڑا اجر ملے گا۔", "RArabic": "INNAL LAZEENA YUBAAYI’OONAKA INNAMAA YUBAAYI’OONAL LAAHA YADUL LAAHI FAWQA AYDEEHIM; FAMAN NAKASA FAINNAMAA YANKUSU ’ALAA NAFSIHEE WA MAN AWFAA BIMAA ’AAHADA ’ALAIHULLAAHA FASA YU’TEEHI AJRAN ’AZEEMAA.", "ArabicText1": "اِنَّ الَّذِيْنَ يُبَايِعُوْنَكَ اِنَّمَا يُبَايِعُوْنَ اللهَ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": "ط ", "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": "يَدُ اللهِ فَوْقَ اَيْدِيْهِمْ", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": "ج ", "ArabicText3": "فَمَن نَّكَثَ فَاِنَّمَا يَنْكُثُ عَلٰى نَفْسِهٖ", "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": "ج ", "ArabicText4": "وَمَنْ اَوْفٰى بِمَا عٰهَدَ عَلَيْهُ اللهَ فَسَيُؤْتِيْهِ اَجْرًا عَظِيْمًا", "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": "ع1", "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016658, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "This verse implicates that the meaning of allegiance here is that firm vow and strong covenant with the Allah and His Messenger (s), and those who fulfilled this covenant, have been promised a great reward. This allegiance will be completed by the following two things…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Yeh aayat bhi is baiyat aur mohkam o ustawaar (mazboot) ahad o paiymaan ki taakeed karti hai jo Khuda aur Uske Rasool (s) ke saath kaha gaya hai aur is ahad ke wafa karne waalo’n ko azeem ajr o sawaab ki khush-khabri deti hai. Yeh baiyat do (2) cheezo’n ke zariye kaamil hogi…", "UrduDescription": "یہ آیہ بتاتی ہے کہ بیعت سے مراد وہی عہد کی تاکید ہے کہ جو خدا اور رسول کے ساتھ ہوا ہے اور اس عہد کو پورا کرنے والوں کو بہت بڑی خوشخبری سنائی گئی ہے۔ یہ بیعت دو چیزوں سے مکمل ہوجاتی ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18":