ove their hands…", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Be-shak jo log aap ki baiy’at (aap se waada) karte hai woh dar-haqeeqat Allah ki baiy’at karte hai aur unke haatho’n ke upar Allah hi ka haath hai…", "Urdu": "اے رسول جو لوگ تیری بیعت کرتے ہیں حقیقت میں خدا کی بیعت کرتے ہیں خدا کا ہاتھ سب ہاتھوں کے اوپر ہے۔۔۔", "RArabic": "INNAL LAZEE-NA YO-BAAYE-O’O-NAKA INNA-MAA YO-BAAYE-O’O-NAL LAAHA YADUL-LAAHE FAWQA AIY-DEE-HIM…", "ArabicText1": "اِنَّ الَّذِيْنَ يُبَايِعُوْنَكَ اِنَّمَا يُبَايِعُوْنَ اللهَ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": "ط ", "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": "يَدُ اللهِ فَوْقَ اَيْدِيْهِمْ۔۔۔", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicT